<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>K. Siema 1977</author>
<hymn_number>265</hymn_number>
<title>Puitu Pathien !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Solomon leh Nehemia Puitu
 Ka lam u-ah Nangmah hung pangin
 Ho-In zawhin a um taa,
 Jerusalem Temple guol khan luohin

[V2]
 Thagau Thiengtho in hun luoh in
 Na min thieng lopina ding leh
 Hatlo te hat thakna dingin
 Vangpiek na'n hun thuomin, Lalpa

[V3]
 2. Na Ho-In thieng sunga hung lut a
 A gitloh nau thupha hung chawia
 Nangmah masang a hung khunte
 Kalvari thisan zalin ngaidam in.

[V4]
 3. Na chanchin Pha thu gentute leh
 Na Ho-In sunga nasemtu te
 Panpihtu nai zing ka Lalpa
 Panpih in Thagau Thiengtho in thuomin

[V5]
 4. Khawvel mite thuneihna ding leh
 Nang helote vaihawmna dingin
 Aw Lalpa, Nangin phal ki'n la
 Vengtu dingin Cherub ka ngen Lalpa.</lyrics>
</song>